headlines.description: — Payton Pritchard scored 27 points, and the Boston Celtics used a big second half to post their 20th victory and roll past the Detroit Pistons 123-99 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Pritchard scores 27 and hits 7 3-pointers to help Celtics earn 20th win, power past Pistons 123-99

headlines.description: — Bam Adebayo had 21 points and 16 rebounds and five assists and the Miami Heat beat the Toronto Raptors 114-104 on Thursday night for their fourth straight victory.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bam Adebayo, Tyler Herro help the Heat beat the Raptors 114-104 for 4th straight victory

events.name: Sacramento Kings at New Orleans Pelicans

headlines.description: — Domantas Sabonas scored a season-high 32 points and matched a season best with 20 rebounds, and the Sacramento Kings beat the New Orleans Pelicans 111-109 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Sabonis has season-high 32 points and 20 rebounds to lead Kings to a 111-109 win over Pelicans
